
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant CampaignService as Campaign Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>UI: Open My/Invited/All campaigns and apply search/filter
    UI->>APIGateway: Get Campaign ( Filter)
    APIGateway->>CampaignService: Forward request + JWT
    CampaignService->>CampaignService: Resolve user from JWT and build scope
    CampaignService->>DB: Query campaign + contributor access + filters + pagination
    DB-->>CampaignService: Campaign rows
    CampaignService-->>APIGateway: 200 list response
    APIGateway-->>UI: Campaign cards/table

    User->>UI: Click expand on one campaign row
    UI->>APIGateway: GET Campaign By Campaign ID
    APIGateway->>CampaignService: Forward request + JWT
    CampaignService->>DB: Query campaign detail by campaignId + access check
    DB-->>CampaignService: Detail row
    CampaignService-->>APIGateway: 200 detail response
    APIGateway-->>UI: Expanded campaign detail
    UI-->>User: Expanded campaign detail
